<paragraph id="1E7C1644BA1EFF8A75B23C56FCE03F6B" blockId="1.[151,1436,1330,1631]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">
Gravenhorst compared this species with 
<taxonomicName id="D9C36DC7BA1EFF8A77623C56FC563C3B" authority="Herbst, 1797" authorityName="Herbst" authorityYear="1797" box="[583,991,1330,1353]" class="Insecta" family="Brentidae" genus="Ischnopterapion" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="virens">
<emphasis id="2CB7CA56BA1EFF8A77623C56FCB43C3B" box="[583,829,1330,1353]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">Ischnopterapion virens</emphasis>
(Herbst, 
<number id="A80B0463BA1EFF8A76843C56FC5E3C3B" box="[929,983,1330,1353]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" value="1797.0">1797</number>
)
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="D9C36DC7BA1EFF8A71363C56FA113C3B" authority="Herbst, 1797" authorityName="Herbst" authorityYear="1797" box="[1043,1432,1330,1353]" class="Insecta" family="Brentidae" genus="Perapion" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="marchicum">
<emphasis id="2CB7CA56BA1EFF8A71363C56FB7A3C3B" box="[1043,1267,1330,1353]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">Perapion marchicum</emphasis>
(Herbst, 
<number id="A80B0463BA1EFF8A70723C56FA193C3B" box="[1367,1424,1330,1353]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" value="1797.0">1797</number>
)
</taxonomicName>
. Despite its very short original description, body sheen and dimension (“nicht völlig eine Linie lang”, and therefore less than 
<quantity id="D93BBBA1BA1EFF8A75F63C1CFED23CFD" box="[211,347,1400,1423]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.25" metricValueMax="2.3" metricValueMin="2.2" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" unit="mm" value="2.25" valueMax="2.3" valueMin="2.2">2.2–2.3 mm</quantity>
long) suggest 
<taxonomicName id="D9C36DC7BA1EFF8A77283C1CFD2C3CFD" box="[525,677,1400,1423]" class="Insecta" family="Apionidae" genus="Apion" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chloris">
<emphasis id="2CB7CA56BA1EFF8A77283C1CFD2C3CFD" box="[525,677,1400,1423]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">Apion chloris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to be conspecific with 
<taxonomicName id="D9C36DC7BA1EFF8A76E63C1CFAFD3CFD" authority="Herbst, 1797" authorityName="Herbst" authorityYear="1797" box="[963,1396,1400,1423]" class="Insecta" family="Brentidae" genus="Ischnopterapion" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="virens">
<emphasis id="2CB7CA56BA1EFF8A76E63C1CFB493CFD" box="[963,1216,1400,1423]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">Ischnopterapion virens</emphasis>
(Herbst, 
<number id="A80B0463BA1EFF8A70163C1CFAE53CFD" box="[1331,1388,1400,1423]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" value="1797.0">1797</number>
)
</taxonomicName>
. In accordance, a specimen of 
<taxonomicName id="D9C36DC7BA1EFF8A749E3CFEFCDF3CC3" authority="Herbst, 1797" authorityName="Herbst" authorityYear="1797" box="[443,854,1434,1457]" class="Insecta" family="Brentidae" genus="Ischnopterapion" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="virens">
<emphasis id="2CB7CA56BA1EFF8A749E3CFEFD3B3CC3" box="[443,690,1434,1457]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">Ischnopterapion virens</emphasis>
(Herbst, 
<number id="A80B0463BA1EFF8A763D3CFEFCC73CC3" box="[792,846,1434,1457]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" value="1797.0">1797</number>
)
</taxonomicName>
is here designated as the 
<typeStatus id="C178A8E6BA1EFF8A71483CFEFB483CC3" box="[1133,1217,1434,1457]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">neotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="D9C36DC7BA1EFF8A71C23CFEFAD93CC3" box="[1255,1360,1434,1457]" class="Insecta" family="Apionidae" genus="Apion" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chloris">
<emphasis id="2CB7CA56BA1EFF8A71C23CFEFAD93CC3" box="[1255,1360,1434,1457]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">A. chloris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. It is a male (fig. 
<number id="A80B0463BA1EFF8A74213CD9FE9B3CA6" box="[260,274,1469,1492]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" value="2.0">2</number>
) labelled: Umg. Berl.: Buch, Coll, Beck / 
<typeStatus id="C178A8E6BA1EFF8A77F63CD9FCC53CA6" box="[723,844,1469,1492]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">NEOTYPE</typeStatus>
<taxonomicName id="D9C36DC7BA1EFF8A76763CD9FB3B3CA6" authority="Gravenhorst, 1807" authorityName="Gravenhorst" authorityYear="1807" box="[851,1202,1469,1492]" class="Insecta" family="Apionidae" genus="Apion" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chloris">
<emphasis id="2CB7CA56BA1EFF8A76763CD9FC6A3CA6" box="[851,995,1469,1492]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">Apion chloris</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="7A526BB5BA1EFF8A76CC3CD9FB3B3CA6" author="Gravenhorst" box="[1001,1202,1469,1492]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" refString="Gravenhorst, I. L. C. (1807) Vergleichende Uebersicht des Linneischen und einiger neuern zoologischen Systeme, nebst dem eigeschalteten Verzeichnisse der zoologischen Sammlungen des Verfassers und den Beschreibungen neuer Thierarten, die in derselben vorhanden sind. Dieterich, Gottingen, XX + 476 pp." type="book" year="1807">
